game_description: Hello and welcome to Speedy Monkeys, S.M is a fan-game inspired by Gorilla Tag! It uses Gorilla Locomotion and the assets/models are hand-made by the owner and developers! Our discord is https://discord.gg/3HX44bzdGc and the link never expires! So what are you waiting for? Download the game and join the amazing community!
review_1: This game is good. It has mods it has many other stuffs, but the only problem is that every time that you go to cities and look for a new cosmetics there’s like an invisible pot that’s surrounded with candles. There is like a cosmetics are going around everywhere and I’m just like “yeah it’s a good game but a lot of issues.” The creator of this game and showed me the game and I was like oh OK I’ll purchase it and yes it’s a very good game and I’m just wondering if he’s reading this hi nice to meet you again.

review_5: This game seems to be a wonderful game, gives you amazing mods. and im sure everyone will agree with me here. this game is great as i have seen, but when i download this game, all i see is “JOiN ThE DisCorD FoR mOrE iNfoRmaTion AboUt SpeeDy MonKEys” with a backround of outer space. i tried to press all the buttons and that didnt work. For me the game was just a room with a background of outer space and text telling me to join the discord. I have no idea how to get in the game and play. Devs, if you see this, please tell me how to get in the game. I still think this is a great game with amazing mods, chill community, and overall just spectacular. But i cant seem to join this game. -monke
